频存储器）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyyu543wlxc","created":1773132003311,"text":"典型的DRFM结构一般包含两个频率转换模块、本地振荡器（LO）、模数转换器（A\\D）、存储模块、数模转换器（D\\A）及控制器。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyyii44k2yo","created":1773131091240,"text":"随着现代战争雷达通信等设备的高频化宽带化，这就对传统基于A\\D的DRFM提出了极高的采样速度要求，同时传统射频器件的工作带宽范围有限，使得数字射频储存器的工作频段受到极大限制。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyxrcuisruo","created":1773128963943,"text":"得益于集成电路和相控阵等的发展等，传统电域探测干扰一体化程度高。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy1u22k2yo","created":1773129785046,"text":"微波光子"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy2myyd6v4","created":1773129847985,"text":"基于微波光子技术我们可以同时实现高频宽带信号的高保真存储和高响应速度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyyizikf6yo","created":1773131129119,"text":"其一体化程度较低，多只承担单一探测或干扰功能。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp16p7fl4o","created":1531797887169,"text":"微波光子技术的优势","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxuynlbq4g","created":1773129246506,"text":"能够实现高分辨率雷达成像","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy00vufzls","created":1773129643179,"text":"微波光子技术由于同时具有光子技术大带宽、抗电磁干扰的特性和微波技术灵活易操控的特性，因而能够实现传统雷达复杂甚至难以实现的宽带微波信号处理与传输，极大提高了雷达系统的距离分辨率，带来了雷达体制新的变革。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy11p18wsg","created":1773129723308,"text":"能够实现高频宽带的干扰"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy6aooksg0","created":1773130134699,"text":"基于微波光子技术的干扰信号产生能够解决数字射频存储器由于工作频段和瞬时带宽受限无法针对敌方雷达产生有效干扰的问题，有效提高雷达的生存能力。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy5viel2ps","created":1773130101668,"text":"成像干扰一体化带来的优势"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy6y000wzk","created":1773130185449,"text":"通过微波光子雷达成像干扰一体化设计，微波光子雷达探测得到的高分辨率成像结果可以用于判断敌方目标的位置、数量和类型等，从而可以根据不同情况选择不同的应对方式以应对复杂的战场环境"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0vi3wjs4","created":1531797862795,"text":"研究内容","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp17ohlswk","created":1531797889303,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18cjbegw","created":1531797890757,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18qmdhs8","created":1531797891608,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp28g7gco4","created":1531797969343,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0w7fnc0k","created":1531797864327,"text":"3. 亮点与不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":47,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp19f2yo84","created":1531797893087,"text":"1. 工作亮点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp19rtkeo8","created":1531797893858,"text":"2. 工作不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0wnpf808","created":1531797865311,"text":"4. 阶段工作规划","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1apwzq8k","created":1531797895919,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1b1h3z4g","created":1531797896618,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1bd2qds8","created":1531797897320,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1brn0xcs","created":1531797898200,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0xg6s1s0","created":1531797867033,"text":"5. 改进建议","layout_right_offset":{"x":61,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1ccip1s8","created":1531797899463,"text":"1. 对公司","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1d52ua04","created":1531797901190,"text":"2. 对部门","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-red-compat","version":"1.4.43"}